Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain　消した記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:16.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely　物語の常が今見せる言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}どうしたって　変えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}目的を忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:32.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:38.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:42.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:47.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:51.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:00.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:09.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:18.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain 抹去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:16.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely 故事總在隻言片語間展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}無論怎麼做都無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}但不要忘記你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:32.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}別人定義出的你 不是真實的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:38.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}堅持自我的力量 才是真的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:42.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}這就是我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:47.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:51.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會回憶走過的路 找出價值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:00.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會堅持到最後 不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:09.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}趁你心裡還亮著一團光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:18.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
